---
// Se agregaron íconos SVG simples para GitHub y LinkedIn
---

<section id="about" class="mx-10 text-center my-6 sm:mx-24">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
    <div
      class="m-auto flex border-violet-800 dark:border-violet-500 rounded-full border-4 w-32 h-32 overflow-hidden shadow-lg"
    >
      <img
        src="/CH-PHOTO.png"
        alt="Profile Photo of Sebastian Albornoz"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="my-5">
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-3xl mb-3 text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-400 font-medium">
        Software Developer 🧑‍💻❤️
      </h3>
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-extralight mb-5">
        Hello! I'm Sebastian Albornoz 🫰
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="text-lg max-w-2xl m-auto text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      <p class="mb-2">
        I'm a Frontend Software Developer with +2 years of experience...
      </p>
      <p class="mb-2">
        I've built many web applications, both independently and for corporate
        clients.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Additionally, I have experience in different skills like video editing,
        image editing, English (B2/C1), and hardware knowledge. Lately, I've
        been learning how to use Unity and coding in C#.
      </p>

      <div class="my-10 bg-violet-50 dark:bg-violet-900/20 p-6 rounded-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl mb-3 text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400 font-bold">
          Present 🎓
        </h2>
        <p>
          I am currently pursuing a degree in "System Analysis" at "Escuela Da
          Vinci", a 3-year program validated as an official technical degree.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="my-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4">
        <!-- Reemplazamos los divs y botones rotos por anclas bien formateadas -->
        <a
          href="/CV.pdf"
          download="Sebastian-Albornoz-CV-Resume.pdf"
          class="bg-violet-800 text-white font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-all hover:bg-violet-700 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg w-full sm:w-auto"
        >
          Download Resume 📄
        </a>
        <a
          href="mailto:sebadevalbornoz@gmail.com"
          class="border-violet-300 text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-300 border-2 font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-all hover:bg-violet-100 dark:hover:bg-violet-900/40 w-full sm:w-auto"
        >
          Talk to me 📧
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Agregamos links a las redes (súper importante para devs) -->
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 mt-6">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Shakkus"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-gray-600 hover:text-violet-600 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:text-violet-400 transition-colors"
          aria-label="GitHub Profile"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sebastian-albornoz-126b90237/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-gray-600 hover:text-violet-600 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:text-violet-400 transition-colors"
          aria-label="LinkedIn Profile"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
